description:
After God completed His work of Creation, He said it was “very good” (Genesis 1:31). Now that sin has marred our world, we see brokenness all around us - even nature itself testifies to that fact as we see death and decay all around us.

But, there is still hope. As we behold the broken aspects of Creation, we can remember that the same God who once made the earth “very good”, has the power to restore it again. 

Watch this #short clip from the Global #Campmeeting sermon, “Believing In Biblical Creation Changes Everything” https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_44S5MBHnjM&list=PL-k2Gb-DBYo9tb9fHW_AxGxJ1R8MpNnpa&index=4 as Timothy Standish encourages us to believe in God’s promise to make all things new. 
—---------------------------------------------------------------------------------
